{"tid":890683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★同游月華撐枱腳　游蕙禎單眼赴會","createTime":"2018-11-05T13:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T14:09:21.000Z","uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1b62ba5ba1fa9bc0fc8231f0b758defafa603746","tid":890683,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181105/photo/bkn-20181105192837096-1105_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181105200802\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181105%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181105192837096-1105_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181105200802&h=ab10e00c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青年新政游蕙禎接連因宣誓風波而遭取消立法會議員資格，和被判非法集結罪成而入獄，事後她漸趨低調，少有公開露面。不過今日(5日)法政匯思游月華就喺Facebook貼咗二人共晉午餐時嘅合照，殊不知唔見游蕙禎一排，佢竟然變咗「獨眼龍」，左眼上貼咗紗布，唔通佢畀人尋仇打腫咗一隻眼？<br />\n<br />\n據悉，游蕙禎係因為做運動受傷，而唔係被尋仇，所以游月華都有祝佢早日康。不過，游蕙禎雖然得番一隻眼，但游月華都直言「影相壓力都幾大，真係讓你一隻眼，都贏你幾條街」，暗讚游蕙禎靚女。話雖如此，游月華喺貼文最後都講「好似姓游嘅女仔普遍都係大眼妹」，唔知佢係咪想講其實自己外表都唔太差呢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181105/bkn-20181105192837096-1105_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181105%2Fbkn-20181105192837096-1105_00822_001.html&d=w5yGqUan81Y6HPaDGCH1WZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8c445b90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181105/bkn-20181105192837096-1105_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d080275823039703b293fdcb59bde5266a0f23f7","tid":890683,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:32:16.000Z","msg":"單眼 游b<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd96b40939210bd0255b0c435bfad1641d4c518","tid":890683,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://